ai-patthana15.67:0.2_0: The Order of the Dhamma: allows unintelligent in the Khadehaka, that is to say, the Lord of the Death,
ai-patthana15.67:0.3_0: Telling over to your limbs, doing good deeds,
ai-patthana15.67:1.1_0: One who doesn’t lead out to the skillful does not give rise to the unskillful, or who has caused the reason.
ai-patthana15.67:1.1_1: Isn’t give rise to skillful qualities, nor have causes and conditions for the sake of their skillful.
ai-patthana15.67:1.1_3: What is not the reason for two reasons.
ai-patthana15.67:2.1_0: Wealthing that is unskillful, nor what is unskillful.
ai-patthana15.67:2.1_3: What are the two kinds of temperament?
